-----> aim_ag_ladders by DamNot <-----


This is the beta release of my first map.

I hope you'll like it and don't forget to leave a comment so I can bring some modifications to it.

Enjoy!




-----> installation instructions <-----

Extract the .rar file and copy/paste the .bsp file into the maps folder
(Steam\SteamApps\YOUR USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps)
